      "span_text": "The muscarinic agonist pilocarpine is known to activate leg CPGs in isolated 323 nervous systems of arthropods [CITATION_1] interactions, we activated the thoracic CPGs by applying pilocarpine to the metathoracic 330 ganglion alone in an in-vitro preparation, and compared the motor output of the different 331 depressor MN pools both with the SEG intact and following its removal.",
